# Classification Rules Sync Policy

When adding, removing, or modifying a classification rule in `src/chimera_sdk/classifier/rules/builtin.py`, you MUST also update `docs/CLASSIFICATION-RULES.md` in the same commit.

Update: Active Rules table, Rule Details section, Metrics Used table if new metrics are referenced.

Source of truth: code in `builtin.py`, docs in `CLASSIFICATION-RULES.md`. Both must match. Divergence is a bug.
